==========================================================
STEP 8.3 - PDF ANALYZER
==========================================================

Created:

app/services/pdf_analyzer.py

Purpose

Analyze every page of the uploaded PDF.

Responsibilities

- Open PDF using PyMuPDF.
- Count pages.
- Extract native text.
- Count characters.
- Compute image coverage ratio.
- Detect page type:
    • NATIVE
    • SCANNED
    • UNKNOWN

Output

One Page object is produced for every PDF page.

==========================================================
STEP 8.4 - PAGE RENDERER
==========================================================

Created:

app/services/page_renderer.py

Purpose

Convert every PDF page into a PNG image.

Responsibilities

- Render pages at 300 DPI.
- Save page images.
- Create the pages folder for each job.

Output

documents/

    pages/

        job_id/

            page_001.png
            page_002.png
            ...

These images will become the common input for all subsequent layers of the pipeline.
